rComments: He clearly loves what he does. I enjoyed everything about this course, even though it was in a 3 hour block per week. The sense of community, the professionalism, the assignments were all great. The way things were designed and the examples made things clear, highly informative and manageable.

The instructor is very well prepared for the class. The course is useful and practical. There are lots of materials I would like to use in my future career. All content are well organized to stimulate students' learning. I like the course a lot and think of the instructor as one of my career models. I really appreciated his enthusiasm.
